NDI(R) SDK v6 — vendored subset for Windows CI and offline builds
==================================================================

This directory contains header files and the x64 static import library
(Processing.NDI.Lib.x64.lib) from the NDI 6 SDK, in the layout expected by
grafton-ndi (include/, lib/x64/).

Distribution: Per Vizrt NDI documentation, NDI SDK header files may be
included in open-source distributions; see:
https://docs.ndi.video/all/developing-with-ndi/sdk/software-distribution
and the NDI SDK License Agreement supplied with the SDK
("NDI SDK License Agreement.pdf").

Trademark: NDI(R) is a registered trademark of Vizrt NDI AB.

Runtime: End users still need the NDI runtime / redistributable as described
in the NDI SDK documentation; this repository does not replace the full SDK
installer for Linux or macOS builds (those platforms continue to resolve the
SDK in CI via .github/actions/setup-ndi-sdk).
